text: Þis is þara fiftig hyda landgemæra to merchamme ærest of eoccan on mæne mor of mæne moere up on hwite more.
Of hwite more on heafoces hamme.
Of tubba forda andlang mores to æppeltune on þone on þone broc of þæn broce on þone pæð.
Of þane paþe on þone ealdan hege of þan ealdan hæge on pyrtan more of pyrtan more þæt eft on eoccan.
